From: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>
Subject: [ALSA] Fix UART enter mode
Patch-mainline: 2.6.24-rc1
References: 

Fixed UART-ENTER command bugs in some MPU-compatible devices.

Signed-off-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

